Proof: The correctness of this lemma follows directly from the definition of productivity.

Now, we want to come up with a data structure that captures all grammar rules and makes it easy for an algorithm to apply the above statement ‚ÄĒ we need to analyze the nature of how exactly the lemma above links productivity of rules. Also, we need to keep in mind that the data structure must be able to express productivity of both productions and non-terminals.

