This algorithm can also be tweaked a bit:


  Breadth first search can be used instead of depth first search.
  Unproductive non-terminals can be detected instead of unproductive rules ‚ÄĒ a non-terminal is productive if it was visited during the depth first search traversal. We can thus analogously build an algorithm that determines productive non-terminals.


